  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_94_6",
    "text": "Secondly, a nows story has to be interesting and unusual. Peaple dont want to read stories about everyday life. As a result, many stories are about some kind of danger and seon the be \"bad\" wews.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
